Update news! Pls. sync your iOS device with iTunes and create a backup before you update your application. v2.3 supports Couple Diary for easy sync. Couple Diary It enables to sync your diary to different devices via server. With your own Diary ID you can sync iPhone iPad or share your diary with friends. NOTE: Be careful that your diary and your friends are mixed after they sync. If you do not want to share your current diary please download and use other MomentDiary family Moment Diary Moment Diary Tale . How to use it! Tap the arrow button on the main page list page and select Couple Diary . Please tap Create new Diary ID when you use for the first time. When you already know a Diary ID please tap Start with known Diary ID . After you setup your Diary ID and Password you can start to sync your diary. Our server deletes your data if no devices access it during 14 days.

Great NEWS! Please make sure to sync your device with iTunes and make backup your device before you update application. MomentDiary v2.2 begins CANDY POINT program!! Now you can earn CANDY point by writing your diary and use it for purchasing various skins or future services at MomentDiary shop!! There are two ways to earn CANDIES. 1. You get 1 CANDY in every time you write a diary. 7 CANDIES DAY at most by this. 2. Install and open other Apps listed on MomentDiary shop. You can earn more money by this!! This version also supports following functions. Color changing of each day on calendar page. Audio data export. CSV file import. You can send a direct message claims or bug reports to developers for quick improvement of MomentDiary. Jump button for the same date of last year or next year. HTTP encoding is used for map links in an export email. Several bugs are fixed. Change display name from MomentDiary to MD . BlueTooth keyboard supported. If you got a trouble with passcode lock just after updating with new version pls. make sure your previous version is not running in the background multitasking . How to check it: 1. Turn your all applications off and go back to home screen. 2. Push home button of your device twice and show multitask icons. 3. If you find MomentDiary or MD in the list please remove the icon. 4. Then please try to restart your MomentDiary once again. We appreciate your feedbacks. Have fun!
